summary: An ordinance relating to and providing for the improvement of Highland Drive, from Dexter Avenue to Westlake Avenue North, in the City of Seattle by constructing a bridge roadway thereon 22 feet in width, all in accordance with Resolution No. 3028 of the city council of the City of Seattle; and providing payment therefor by the mode of "Payment in Bonds", as provided by the laws of the State of Washington and the Charter and Ordinances of the City of Seattle.
